beginning; containing an area of FIVE HUNDRED TWENTY EIGHT THOUSAND EIGHT HUNDRED THIRTY-THREE (528,833) Square Meters, more or less.

NOTE: This technical description is subject to future survey.”

Proclamation No. 234 dated December 19, 1955, is hereby revoked.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 4th day of October, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and sixty-seven.

(SGD.) FERDINAND E. MARCOS President of the Philippines

By the President: (SGD.) RAFAEL M. SALAS Executive Secretary

